00:01:00,080 --> 00:01:01,360
You deserve to die.

2
00:01:01,880 --> 00:01:03,280
You deserve to die.

3
00:01:03,760 --> 00:01:05,239
You deserve to die.

4
00:01:05,680 --> 00:01:07,040
You deserve to die.

5
00:01:07,680 --> 00:01:09,000
I'm sorry, I'm sorry. Damn it.

6
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:11,320
I was wrong. I'm sorry. Damn it.

7
00:01:11,520 --> 00:01:12,680
I'm sorry. I was wrong.

8
00:01:12,680 --> 00:01:14,600
I'm sorry, I'm sorry. Please forgive me.

9
00:01:15,920 --> 00:01:16,720
You mean...

10
00:01:16,880 --> 00:01:18,480
Liu Liu wanted to get revenge on Boss Qi?

11
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:21,280
It's just a guess.

12
00:01:21,680 --> 00:01:23,160
Because I clearly remember,

13
00:01:24,240 --> 00:01:25,920
when she split into Yaoyao,

14
00:01:26,560 --> 00:01:27,520
I asked her.

15
00:01:28,560 --> 00:01:30,960
She never had any thought of revenge.

16
00:01:31,680 --> 00:01:33,160
She just wanted to protect Liu Liu.

17
00:01:34,200 --> 00:01:35,720
But when she became Liu Liu,

18
00:01:37,560 --> 00:01:39,160
she told me more than once

19
00:01:39,560 --> 00:01:41,320
that Yaoyao wanted revenge.

20
00:01:43,840 --> 00:01:44,640
Oh, right.

21
00:01:46,720 --> 00:01:48,920
Qi Xiaoyu said someone gave him this charm.

22
00:01:49,240 --> 00:01:50,320
Take a look. What is this?

23
00:01:52,240 --> 00:01:53,040
This...

24
00:01:54,480 --> 00:01:55,840
This is a Daji charm.

25
00:01:57,360 --> 00:01:58,280
From Daji.

26
00:02:00,280 --> 00:02:01,200
This charm...

27
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:04,160
There's nothing wrong with it.

28
00:02:09,240 --> 00:02:10,520
Damn it.

29
00:02:13,640 --> 00:02:14,960
Do you know what "paihuazi" is?

30
00:02:17,320 --> 00:02:18,280
A long time ago,

31
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:19,760
there was a group of people

32
00:02:20,280 --> 00:02:22,480
who smeared drugs on objects,

33
00:02:22,880 --> 00:02:24,240
and then used those objects

34
00:02:25,080 --> 00:02:26,640
to abduct women and children,

35
00:02:27,320 --> 00:02:28,720
and extort money.

36
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:31,360
Doing such heartless, immoral things.

37
00:02:32,640 --> 00:02:33,520
Are you saying

38
00:02:35,640 --> 00:02:36,920
that Liu Liu did this?

39
00:02:36,920 --> 00:02:37,560
No.

40
00:02:38,760 --> 00:02:40,480
You've known Liu Liu for so long.

41
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:42,280
You should trust her.

42
00:02:44,240 --> 00:02:46,480
Even though Liu Liu suffers from her condition,

43
00:02:47,080 --> 00:02:49,000
she would never do something like this.

44
00:02:49,600 --> 00:02:50,800
Of course I trust her.

45
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:51,440
But...

46
00:02:53,920 --> 00:02:54,720
Uncle Wang.

47
00:02:55,200 --> 00:02:56,840
Let's have another proper talk with Liu Liu.

48
00:02:56,920 --> 00:02:59,040
You're not hearing me, are you?

49
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:03,560
Listen to me,

50
00:03:04,040 --> 00:03:06,680
her condition takes time to heal.

51
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:08,800
If you go to her now

52
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:10,120
and provoke her,

53
00:03:10,480 --> 00:03:12,400
what if she does something extreme?

54
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:15,800
Besides, this charm

55
00:03:17,040 --> 00:03:18,800
might not have been taken by Liu Liu.

56
00:03:19,880 --> 00:03:21,160
Don't overthink it.

57
00:03:21,720 --> 00:03:22,520
But...

58
00:03:22,720 --> 00:03:23,600
But Liu Liu...

59
00:03:24,280 --> 00:03:25,080
Enough.

60
00:03:28,200 --> 00:03:29,400
Daji is gone now.

61
00:03:30,160 --> 00:03:31,080
Look at Zhou Yi.

62
00:03:31,320 --> 00:03:32,840
He's already ended up like this.

63
00:03:34,400 --> 00:03:36,000
How can I think about anything else?

64
00:03:39,240 --> 00:03:40,040
Uncle Wang.

65
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:43,640
Zhou Yi still has Sister Bai.

66
00:03:44,760 --> 00:03:45,680
But what about Liu Liu?

67
00:03:46,120 --> 00:03:47,600
Liu Liu only has us.

68
00:03:48,320 --> 00:03:49,680
She trusts you so much.

69
00:03:50,040 --> 00:03:51,520
She considers you family!

70
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:55,200
I already said,

71
00:03:55,840 --> 00:03:58,360
her condition needs time to heal.

72
00:03:59,600 --> 00:04:00,600
I trust Liu Liu.

73
00:04:01,720 --> 00:04:03,080
She'll figure it out.

74
00:04:03,240 --> 00:04:04,040
Old Wang.

75
00:04:06,160 --> 00:04:08,360
You sold Daji and took Wu Qianchen's money.

76
00:04:08,720 --> 00:04:10,840
You want to wash your hands of it all?

77
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:12,560
You're being so irresponsible!

78
00:04:18,200 --> 00:04:19,279
What do you want?

79
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:21,560
What the hell do you want?

80
00:04:24,280 --> 00:04:25,600
I'm irresponsible?

81
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:26,960
I'm irresponsible?

82
00:04:27,960 --> 00:04:29,120
If it weren't for you guys

83
00:04:29,440 --> 00:04:30,760
taking on side jobs behind my back,

84
00:04:31,120 --> 00:04:32,600
taking Zhou Yi to Jixiang Village,

85
00:04:32,880 --> 00:04:34,240
would I be getting threatened?

86
00:04:34,440 --> 00:04:36,240
Would Zhou Yi be in the hospital?

87
00:04:39,080 --> 00:04:40,320
Are you being responsible?

88
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:43,480
Who have you ever been responsible for?

89
00:04:46,000 --> 00:04:47,120
Do you even know?

90
00:04:47,680 --> 00:04:48,520
If back then,

91
00:04:48,520 --> 00:04:49,960
I hadn't gone along with Liu Liu

92
00:04:50,160 --> 00:04:51,520
and kept her by my side,

93
00:04:52,480 --> 00:04:54,280
do you know what would've happened to her?

94
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:56,520
She'd be in a mental hospital.

95
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:58,400
And you,

96
00:04:59,440 --> 00:05:00,640
if I hadn't taken you in,

97
00:05:00,640 --> 00:05:01,480
where would you be now?

98
00:05:16,640 --> 00:05:18,120
Daji isn't your home.

99
00:05:20,960 --> 00:05:22,600
Go do whatever you want.

100
00:06:28,400 --> 00:06:29,080
Liu Liu

101
00:07:17,760 --> 00:07:18,760
No one's here,

102
00:07:19,840 --> 00:07:20,920
but the door's wide open.

103
00:07:22,640 --> 00:07:24,280
And Boss Qi isn't picking up either.

104
00:07:26,520 --> 00:07:27,600
Could something really have happened?

105
00:08:53,760 --> 00:09:18,400
I'm sorry, I'm sorry, I'm sorry.

106
00:09:18,400 --> 00:09:19,760
Long time no see.

107
00:09:20,080 --> 00:09:20,880
Boss Qi.

108
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:23,880
It's you. It's you.

109
00:09:24,360 --> 00:09:26,040
I'm sorry, I'm sorry.

110
00:09:26,320 --> 00:09:28,080
I was wrong. I'm sorry.

111
00:09:28,440 --> 00:09:29,600
I'm sorry.

112
00:09:31,400 --> 00:09:32,440
Family, please wait outside.

113
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:51,640
What are you doing here?

114
00:09:54,480 --> 00:09:56,000
I already gave you the land.

115
00:09:56,120 --> 00:09:57,400
What more do you want?

116
00:09:58,000 --> 00:09:58,880
Boss Wang.

117
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:01,560
Don't get so worked up.

118
00:10:02,800 --> 00:10:04,600
I just came to see Zhou Yi.

119
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:08,160
Since your gods and ghosts can't save him,

120
00:10:09,520 --> 00:10:10,920
I should be able to.

121
00:10:24,080 --> 00:10:25,440
Something this good,

122
00:10:26,760 --> 00:10:29,240
Lin You and I never had it as kids.

123
00:10:49,520 --> 00:10:50,320
Boss Wang

124
00:10:52,280 --> 00:10:53,080
Take it easy

125
00:10:56,720 --> 00:10:57,880
Have some more fruit

126
00:10:58,480 --> 00:10:59,600
Don't let it go to waste

127
00:11:59,280 --> 00:12:00,080
Boss Qi.

128
00:12:04,200 --> 00:12:05,000
Boss Qi.

129
00:12:33,640 --> 00:12:34,440
Boss Qi

130
